                        </div>
                        <div class="featured-cars-txt">
                            <h2>Jaguar XF</h2><h3>$180,000</h3>
                            <p>Slim and striking with Front Animated Directional Indicators. Gloss Black foil on the monogram-patterned grille mesh emphasises elegance.</p>
